<br />
<br /> I thought I had a thread here about these. Guest not. Anyway, these are NES roms running on PCE hardware with small amount of hacking and ton of realtime video/audio emulation. Blah-blah-blah. I added a couple of games to the list.
<br />
<br /> MottZilla, did you ever get Contra up and running? If you've abandoned the project, mind if I try? I have some downtime coming up and plan to go through some of the other MMC1/UNROM games for projects.

		

